#  Royal Enfield Inspired Website

A static website inspired by the Royal Enfield brand, built using HTML AND CSS.

## Features

- Responsive Navigation Bar
- Hero Section
- Motorcycles Showcase
- Riding Gear & Accessories Section
- About Section
- Contact Section
- Cart Section
- Smooth Scrolling Navigation
- Hover Effects and Animations

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox
- CSS Transitions
- CSS Transformations

## Project Structure

```
├── index.html
├── style.css
└── Images/
```

## How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open `index.html` in a web browser.

